description: Experience elevated urban living from the 19th floor of Echelon - where luxury meets lifestyle. This 2 bed, 2 bath residence is beautifully curated with floor-to-ceiling windows filling the space with natural light, wide-plank oak floors, a chef-inspired kitchen with integrated Thermidor appliances and Italian cabinetry and picture-perfect views of the Boston skyline. The primary suite offers a spa-like retreat with a marble-clad bathroom, custom walk-in closet and a Juliet balcony to soak in the views. The second bedroom is a perfect flex space with a custom built-in Murphy Bed great for guests or home office. This full-service, luxury property features 3 resort-style pools, 24/7 concierge, on-site fitness center with basketball court, golf simulator, numerous lounges and outdoor terraces - over 50,000 sqft of amenities. Located in the heart of Boston’s Seaport, you’re surrounded by world-class restaurants, designer boutiques and waterfront parks. Property sold "As-is".
